review_blob: One of the best beers i have ever tasted . One Year lagered on winebarrels and one year on bourbon barrels ! Almost divine !
Nice hoppy beer with citrus tones maybe missing a little warmth from alcohol, drinks easy and i think its a beer for all times !
Nice triple ipa taste is smooth bitterness with a taste of american hops ! I like the taste and colour wich is Amber !
A little sweet , red fruit tones and caramel , nice colour and scent , nice and little sweet barley wine ! I like it !!
beer_name: Flying Dog Horn Dog Barley Wine

review_blob: Nice beer , first you taste a lot of hop , it gives a nice sensation in your mouth. Bitterness at the end . Not for everybody i think.
Nice beer with chocolate and caramel tones , lots of flavor and great smell !
